title: Vegetation health Index (VHI)
description:
I recently experimented with generating the Vegetation Health Index (VHI) for the Tamale Metropolitan Area using ModelBuilder in ArcGIS Pro.
The process involved calculating:
NDVI - for vegetation greenness
LST - Land Surface Temperature
VCI (Vegetation Condition Index) - highlights how green or healthy the vegetation is compared to normal
TCI (Temperature Condition Index) - shows how temperature stress affects vegetation
These inputs were combined to create a VHI, helping visualize vegetation health across the region.
